    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You run a <strong>delivery service</strong> with your friends, aiming to complete as <strong>many deliveries</strong> as possible to earn enough money to <strong>pay the rent</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231300/extras/f695139335a15dec7248c5f7612d0de5.poster.avif?t=1749052981\" width=614 height=248 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231300/extras/f695139335a15dec7248c5f7612d0de5.webm?t=1749052981\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231300/extras/f695139335a15dec7248c5f7612d0de5.mp4?t=1749052981\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>The city is<strong> alive</strong>, with people and cars around the streets. But these might <strong>not be the only inhabitants</strong> of the city.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231300/extras/a8f3afecad6d74fdd2eba1280457e2bb.poster.avif?t=1749052981\" width=614 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231300/extras/a8f3afecad6d74fdd2eba1280457e2bb.webm?t=1749052981\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231300/extras/a8f3afecad6d74fdd2eba1280457e2bb.mp4?t=1749052981\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>Communicate</strong> through<strong> proximity voice chat </strong>or by <strong>using the radio</strong> on your bike. <strong>Don't</strong> stray too far from it if you want to stay connected with your teammates, as getting lost is easy and you might become the unfortunate <strong>victim</strong> of an accident.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231300/extras/a7925d20ae3469df76935f97d7928a13.poster.avif?t=1749052981\" width=614 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231300/extras/a7925d20ae3469df76935f97d7928a13.webm?t=1749052981\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231300/extras/a7925d20ae3469df76935f97d7928a13.mp4?t=1749052981\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Always remember to pay the rent; we don't want to anger our landlord, <strong>s̵̝̰̥͑̂î̵̲͕̜́͆n̸̼͠c̵̠̈́̉ȩ̸̿ ̸̲̫́h̵̬̮̄̅̎e̸̞̖̊ͅ ̵͔̊ĭ̸͔̼s̷̗͌̅͗ ̵̔́̀͜s̴̙͇̥͒ö̵͍̙́ ̸̳̍̔n̷͖̂i̴̹̠̔̍̄c̷̢̱̻̅͒̕ȩ̷̤̄́̈!̷̖̲̐̓</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231300/extras/ef5c46ea6f9ef40f0c6f2385a3e40d96.poster.avif?t=1749052981\" width=614 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231300/extras/ef5c46ea6f9ef40f0c6f2385a3e40d96.webm?t=1749052981\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231300/extras/ef5c46ea6f9ef40f0c6f2385a3e40d96.mp4?t=1749052981\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>UNCOVER THE SECRETS</strong>Learn about the monsters and the lore around the city, <i>what happened to all of them?</i><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231300/extras/79da4a44d6490068927669eff52083ef.poster.avif?t=1749052981\" width=800 height=558 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231300/extras/79da4a44d6490068927669eff52083ef.webm?t=1749052981\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231300/extras/79da4a44d6490068927669eff52083ef.mp4?t=1749052981\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
